Data set: PlynlimonVegSoilTable

PlynlimonVegSoilTable is a look-up table for vegetation and soil classes.

data("PlynlimonVegSoilTable")

Format

A data frame with 58 rows and the following 12 columns:

Class
Description of vegetation class
SubClass
Description of vegetation subclass
LCM2007Class
Corresponding class in Land Cover Map 2007
LCM2007SubClass
Corresponding subclass in Land Cover Map 2007
LCM2000Class
Corresponding class in Land Cover Map 2000
LCM2000SubClass
Corresponding subclass in Land Cover Map 2000
LCM1990SubClass
Corresponding subclass in Land Cover Map 1990
VEG2013SubClass
Corresponding subclass in Vegetation Map 2013
SoilA
CN value for soil type A
SoilB
CN value for soil type B
SoilC
CN value for soil type C
SoilD
CN value for soil type D

Source

http://hdl.handle.net/10044/1/30773

References

Vitolo, C. (2015), Exploring data mining for hydrological modelling (Ph.D. thesis), Imperial College London, uri: http://hdl.handle.net/10044/1/30773.
